title: David Beckham gets rose tattoo on his neck
text:
David Beckham gets rose tattoo on his neck 
Irish Examiner Friday 23rd October, 2015 
David Beckham has got a new tattoo of a rose on his neck. The former soccer star, 40, has had the delicate shaded flower and stem, featuring three leaves, etched on the lefthand side of his skin down towards his collar bone. His wife Victoria, 41, took to her Instagram account on Friday (23.10.15) to share a snap of her hunky husband lapping up the sun in Los Angeles flaunting his new inking....
